        "name": "APIs.io API",
        "description": "Read-only discovery API over the APIs.io catalog — search and browse APIs, providers, tags, industries, regions, areas, ratings, and 17 published artifact types. Every operation maps 1:1 to an MCP tool and, where one exists, an Agent Skill (the API → MCP → Agent-Skill experience chain). Raw discovery (search, providers, apis, tags, all artifact collections) is free; curated dimensions (industries/regions/areas), rating data, and synthesis (compare/gaps/changes/stack) are Pro. Per-operation tier + tool + skill are declared in the OpenAPI via x-tier / x-mcp-tool / x-agent-skill (see the x-apis-io map).",
        "humanURL": "https://apis.io/developer/",
        "baseURL": "https://apis.io/api/v1",
